Cross-Device Reports under Audience to see how authenticated users behave across devices. 
The first report is the Device Overlap report.

Device Overlap helps you understand how many users viewed your site on desktop, tablet, and mobile. 
It can also give you a sense of how many users access your site with more than one device.

The Device Paths report shows the sequence of device categories used to view your content. 
This can help you discover the order that people tend to move between devices. 
